0.1.2.name: connect20/Fancy_Product_Compare
0.1.2.description: Fancy Product Compare Magento extension allows the visitors on your Magento store to compare the products in a very convenient way. Product comparison is done in a fancy popup window where user can add the product to cart or wishlist.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
